OL,6,FCourts will sit for extra days to help
OL,7,Ftackle backlogs, the Deputy Prime
OL,8,FMinister is set to announce, as judges
OL,9,Fare forced to apologise for justice
OL,10,Fdelays.
OL,12,FDavid Lammy will announce plans for
OL,13,Fvictims to get faster justice in a
OL,14,Fspeech on Wednesday, with the
OL,15,FGovernment funding an extra 1,250
OL,16,Fsitting days.
