OL,3,CCourts will sit for extra days to
OL,4,Ctackle growing backlog
OL,6,FThe speech, which coincides with the
OL,7,Fopening of the legal year, comes as
OL,8,Fseveral judges have apologised to
OL,9,Fdefendants and victims for delays in
OL,10,Fthe court system, with some trials
OL,11,Fpushed back multiple years.
OL,13,FThe Government has said the plans will
OL,14,Fensure more trials can be heard to
OL,15,Fhelp tackle the growing backlog of
OL,16,Fcases.
