OL,3,CCourts will sit for extra days to
OL,4,Ctackle growing backlog
OL,6,FAlso on Tuesday, seven defendants
OL,7,Fallegedly involved in an attack in a
OL,8,Fpark in Peterlee were told they faced
OL,9,Fa two-and-a-half-year delay before
OL,10,Ftheir trial, which is set for March
OL,11,F2028.
OL,13,FJudge Richard Clews told the group,
OL,14,Fwho all pleaded not guilty, that there
OL,15,Fis a "substantial backlog" in the
OL,16,Fcourt.
OL,18,FMr Lammy said: "The crown court
OL,19,Fbacklog we inherited stands at over
OL,20,F78,000 and behind each case is a real
OL,21,Fperson, waiting years for justice.
