OL,6,F"That is why we are acting with the
OL,7,Fbiggest investment on record as part
OL,8,Fof our plan for change.
OL,10,F"An additional 1,250 sitting days will
OL,11,Fbe allocated to the crown court this
OL,12,Ffinancial year, allowing it to hear
OL,13,Fmany extra cases.
OL,15,F"We know there is more to do, and
OL,16,Fgenerational reform that cannot wait,
OL,17,Fbut this investment will help ease the
OL,18,Ftorment and bring swifter justice to
OL,19,Fmany more victims."
