OL,6,FThe Law Society welcomed the move as a
OL,7,F"welcome step forward" but stressed
OL,8,Finvestment is needed across the whole
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,FRichard Atkinson, president of the Law
OL,12,FSociety of England and Wales, said:
OL,13,F"Further action remains crucial to
OL,14,Ftackle the crown court backlogs in the
OL,15,Flonger-term, as well as to address the
OL,16,Frecord backlogs in the magistrates
OL,17,Fcourt.
OL,19,F"The Government needs to ensure
OL,20,Fimprovements in one part of the system
OL,21,Fcan be matched throughout the pipeline.
